metadata.name: Block Quest PassKey
metadata.description:
This Block Quest PassKey allows entry to the token gated "Area 23" of Flagship

Add this NFT in your wallet connected to your Spatial.io account.

Enter Flagship Area-23 at this link  
https://www.spatial.io/s/FLAGSHIP-Area-23-63703ba4e051b600011c6826?share=2150419419978192999

The first clue is right in front of you. What a GEM! Something of this nature can only be from the Biess Galaxy in the outer rim of Flagship floor levels. This gem is known as the "threeINAkind" Diamonde and was one of two sisters discovered in the  Geffuktogon Mountains. Her sister was listed on the market and holds a wealth of knowledge in it's detail. Definitely worth taking a look. 

The location of PassKey#4 may be buried deep in the core of the gem's history. Then again, it might be another missing piece to collect in order to complete this quest. 

Remember, the only transactions required to complete "The Elements" quest are the Block Quest PassKeys.   

Good Luck.  
etherstu
